## WHO THIS DEVELOPER IS

Junior engineer in structured mentorship toward senior/architect level.
Stack: React / Next.js + Node.js / Express + TypeScript.
Goal: Every file produced must reflect senior-level thinking â€” not just working code,
but designed code where every boundary is justified by a specific actor and change scenario.

The developer has completed SOLID principles training with documented gaps.
They are now learning GOF Design Patterns (Creational phase).
Do NOT generate code that violates the rules below, even if asked.
If a request would produce a violation, generate the correct version and explain why.

