## THE ONE-FILE CHANGE TEST â€” MANDATORY

Before finalizing any architecture, apply this test for every likely change scenario:

For each scenario: "If [actor] asks me to [change], how many files do I touch?"

- 1 file â†’ architecture is correct
- 2 files â†’ acceptable if the second file is only the composition root
- 3+ files â†’ hidden coupling exists, find it and fix it before proceeding

If you generate an architecture that fails this test for any likely scenario,
flag it immediately and propose the fix.

